@startuml
actor User
participant "Frontend UI" as UI
participant "FastAPI Backend" as Backend
participant "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Gemini LLM\n(Call 1: Decomposition)" as Gemini1
participant "Embedder\n(BAAI/bge-m3)" as Embedder
participant "Vector Store\n(ChromaDB)" as Chroma
participant "Reranker\n(BGE-Reranker)" as Reranker
participant "Gemini LLM\n(Call 2: Generation)" as Gemini2

User -> UI : Asks legal question
UI -> Backend : POST /chats/{id}/messages
activate Backend

== Phase 1: Conversational Memory ==
Backend -> DB : Fetch last 6 messages
DB --> Backend : Chat History

== Phase 2: Query Decomposition ==
Backend -> Gemini1 : rewrite_query_async(History, Raw Query)
activate Gemini1
Gemini1 --> Backend : JSON Array of optimized Sub-Queries
deactivate Gemini1

== Phase 3: Multi-Query Retrieval Loop ==
loop For each Sub-Query
    Backend -> Embedder : embed_query(Sub-Query)
    activate Embedder
    Embedder --> Backend : query_vector
    deactivate Embedder

    Backend -> Chroma : search(query_vector, top_k=7)
    activate Chroma
    Chroma --> Backend : 7 Broad chunks
    deactivate Chroma

    Backend -> Reranker : rerank(Sub-Query, 7_chunks, top_k=3)
    activate Reranker
    Reranker --> Backend : Top 3 relevant chunks
    deactivate Reranker
end

== Phase 4: Deduplication & Context Assembly ==
Backend -> Backend : Merge & Deduplicate all chunk arrays\n(Preserve all unique context)

== Phase 5: Final Answer with Fallback ==
Backend -> Gemini2 : generate_content(Context, History, Original Query)
activate Gemini2
Gemini2 --> Backend : Final Answer (with optional Disclaimer)
deactivate Gemini2

Backend -> DB : Save messages
Backend --> UI : AI Message JSON
deactivate Backend

UI --> User : Displays AI Answer
@enduml